Charles Thomas Shad, Law Offices of S. Perry Penland, Jacksonville, Fla., for plaintiff-appellant. John Wilbur, Milam, Ramsay, Martin & Ade, Jacksonville, Fla., for defendantappellee.

Affirmed. See Local Rule 21.1
